Agreement between the European Union and Japan for an Economic Partnership - Articles 2.28 and 2.35
DECISION No 1/2019 OF THE EU-JAPAN WORKING GROUP ON WINE on the adoption of the forms to be used for certificates for the import of wine products originating in Japan into the European Union and the modalities concerning self-certification:
- The form to be used for certificates authenticated in conformity with the laws and regulations of Japan is set out in Annex I to this Decision - Simplified VI 1 - Certificate issued by the national research institute of brewing [NRIB] for the imports of wine products originating in Japan into the EU.
The form to be used for self-certificates established by producers authorised by the competent authority of Japan is set out in Annex II to this Decision - Simplified VI 1 - Self-Certificate for the Imports of Wine Products Originating in Japan into the European Union.
